name: Commit Crimes - Youth #1
description:
"Commit Crimes" is a remembrance that being young is about living life with attitude and doing the things you love even though people may not understand it. Do what makes you happy, make art, make mistakes. Commit crimes if you want to. Do not listen to people that portray you as a criminal. Following the law doesn't make you a good person. Breaking the law doesn't make you a bad one.

"Youth" is a motivational series for all the fucked up kids. It's about growing up and not fitting in people expectations. Lightly influenced by Euphoria new season.
